Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:43.91,CN_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(150,150)}寻寻觅觅 今天也将{\c&HBFC3F4&}继{\c&HD8F5E1&}续前进
