Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:06.76,CN_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(150,150)}无法忘记那珍{\c&HBFC3F4&}贵{\c&HD8F5E1&}的 点点滴滴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:14.75,CN_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(150,150)}只{\c&HBFC3F4&}希{\c&HD8F5E1&}望有一天 能传达给你
